"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-04-team-gb-star-first-ever-win-olympic-medal-male-female-events-21357620\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Henry Fieldman became the first person in the history of theOlympicsto win a medal in both men's and women's events, thanks to his bronze in the women's eight.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Fieldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Henry Fieldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Fieldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Fieldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This came after he claimed bronze in Tokyo in the men's eight three years ago and he now holds a unique place in Olympic history.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9412830928174368, \"rank\": 0.062262372911056824, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This came about as Fieldman is a coxswain and, thanks to a rule change in 2017, the coxswain can compete in the boat with eithergender.\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The cox steers the boat from the stern and calls the strokes, facing the rowers as they help implement strategy.\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit said of his achievement: 'They only changed the rule in 2017 so someone was going to do it and it just happened to be me.'\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was clearly thrilled with the success, despite the humble response, saying: 'It's been a real joy, the honour of my life.'\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old added after the women's bronze: 'I hope that now that we have had two Olympic medals in the women's eight that this could be the start of more women's eights medals to come - stepping on to greater things.'\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Romania claimed gold in the women's eight, with Canada taking silver ahead of Great Britain.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"score\": 0.9769044219766124, \"rank\": 0.022628108113659003, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 1075, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.7280312532682872, \"rank\": 0.33092092191095923, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9879144483218082, \"rank\": 0.012230342288200982, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an even better day for the men's eight on Saturday as the team won gold in Paris, with Netherlands taking silver and USA bronze.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1203, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999993840447, \"rank\": 6.158726683752812e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9847222379013635, \"rank\": 0.01039470193399492, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9926489643216665, \"rank\": 0.007394276106588543, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow the latest news from Paris 2024 with Metro.co.uk's Olympics live blog.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.624352864790848e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"score\": 0.9993608704165835, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Metro.co.uk\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cox Harry Brightmore said: 'It was one hell of a ride back at the end of the boat.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We knew the start would be close - the American guys giving it a quite a lot of shouting on the start line, which we were ready for.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999951097219285, \"rank\": 3.0830671775847763e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That was a bit of a sprint to the death, we just took it by the scruff of the neck and you can not really ask for much more.'\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Boxer Lin Yu Ting secures Olympic medal after gender row  ArrowMORE:My fianc\\u00e9 wants to watch the Olympics on his phone at our friends' wedding  ArrowMORE:Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce posts emotional statement after shock Olympics 100m withdrawal  Your guide to the week in football.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exclusive analysis, FPL tips and transfer talk - sign up, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": []}]}"